author: @by_joy
text:
Hi my love
I missed you
How are you? Are you tired?
I keep thinking about you every day.
Most of the time I think about you for random things. I see things you like, I hear a song and think you would love it.
They say that what makes a place beautiful is the sensitivity of the person who sees it.
I distract myself watching the wind blowing through the leaves and the raindrops on the window.
And when I look at the sky, I wonder if the moon is appearing for you tonight.
Even with time passing, I am happy to feel that my life has you by my side.
That I can see what you paint, I can see your smile and we grow older.
Thank you for today's gift and for all the gifts you give me every day for being my Hwang Hyunjin.

author: @by_joy
text:
I wanted to announce to the world the happiness that fills me
but deep down
the happier I became
the less the world was interested
maybe they would resent it
it's not about being happy
it's not about talking about the curvy line of your nose and  how I can't stop thinking about it
and I like it when you turn your head because I just wanna stop and draw it
it's comfortable to be in silence by your side
but I need to get this out of my system
because it's simply so huge
that I can't contain it
I can tell you every day
would you get tired?
I'm not interested in containing myself
I don't want to brag
so I come to write
and whoever reads
will know that you are my love

It feels like a song of free love.
 Free love is a very difficult thing.
 As much as you give, people often ask for a reward.
 Since I did ã€‡ã€‡, I paid a lot of money...
 There must be many reasons, feelings, and thoughts...
 However, criticism and denial always seem to bother each other.
 I pray that expressions such as music, singing, and dancing will sublimate them.

author: @amywithsnakes
text:
Its been 4 months and this song still brings me to tears with just the beginning melody. 

For me this feels like longing for the person one used to be. We all change as we age- we become two different people even though we share the same body.

I constantly look back at my younger self, I was happier, I smiled more, I experienced and explored life. Presently I have little to no motivation to do even basic errands, I struggle to maintain friendships, true smiling and happiness doesn't come easy. I constantly miss who I used to be.

Thank you, Hyunjin, for turning poetry and art into beautiful music and lyrics.

author: @Cherrrryssspoison
text: I love you, Hwang Hyunjin, with all my soul. I love you not only as a talented idol, not only as a media personality, not only as a person who only entertains others by memorizing the script, but as you, the real you: you smiling, you laughing, rejoicing in all sorts of little things, drawing amazing drawings that sometimes reflect your mental anguish, but there is something in them something native, something that gives hope that our emotions and experiences are similar. I love you dancing so that your soul draws smooth and refined movements, from which it is impossible to take your eyes off. I have little chance of even getting to the concert, but despite the fact that our meeting will not happen soon or never, I will still love and appreciate you. Looking at how you try to improve yourself day after day, feeling your scrupulous love for us, for Stay, I want to give you all the most beautiful things in this world, because you deserve it. Please remember that the world is full of love and you deserve it in full. Feel it every day. Keep shining not only for the world, but also for yourself, for your loved ones. Appreciate your efforts and know that you are doing enough. Even if I'm just a stupid sixteen-year-old Stay, even if I can't even get to one of the concerts and feel real happiness with a boiling heart, even if you don't know about my existence, even if you feel unimportant on certain days, even if you have a loved one to whom you are ready to give yourself I will still love, appreciate and respect you with the lightest love in the world, you will still unconsciously give me faith for the best, you will still be my motivation and inspiration for great deeds. I'm proud of you, okay? And I will always be on your side. Thank you so much, thank you for being there, thank you for being alive and well, thank you for sharing your love with the world, thank you for being so sincere, thank you for your healing voice, thank you.Thank you and 2022 for introducing me to you. Be healthy, happy and loved. I love you, Hwang Hyunjin. You make me alive, you make me real StayğŸ«‚â¤ï¸â€ğŸ©¹

author: @h-playwithmyhart.4806
text: Hyunjin. It was certainly your musicality that drew me to you first. You have such a playful but easy tone which highlights and gives definition to every Stray Kids song. You donâ€™t have fixated or set rapping style. You are very experimental vocally and lyrically and Iâ€™ve found myself charmed by your voice due the versatility of it. I also love your singing style for similar reasons. You are just as diverse of a singer as you are rapper. It is really peaceful and harmonious; and blends perfectly with the rest of your members. I love how you donâ€™t hold anything back when youâ€™re singing and I can really feel the emotion and work that you pour into each line that you sing. Similarly to your singing and rapping, your body knows no limits when you are met with a choreography. You dance with a ferocity and a passion that no other performers can possess. You take each choreography and sincerely make it your own, which is honestly a blessing to watch. When you are dancing, you can be yourself and express your emotions with the beauty of your body movements. You can lose yourself easily into your dance and you are so comfortable and trusting of your own abilities. For this generation specifically, you have transformed music and given new meaning to what it can and should do for people. You are changing the world each day that you continue to share your artistry and dance; and we are so lucky to be alive right now to get to be a part of the history that youâ€™re making. At the same time that I love your music and dance, I love your personality as well. I love that sometimes you keep to yourself, but other times, you are goofy and outgoing. As I mentioned before, you are extremely freeing to be around and those who spend time with you can relax and be themselves in your presence. I know that nobody can attest to these qualities quite like your members. Seven different personalities, and they all love you and cherish you for their own special reasons. Theyâ€™ve looked to you and have modeled their perseverance off of how you strive to not let the difficult times hold you down and prevent you from success. You have opened your heart up to all seven people, although you come from different backgrounds, and that has encouraged them to all to have such a loving relationship with one another. Youâ€™ve had love for them since you began your journey with them and this has establishing a lifelong love that all of you had before you even debuted. You see the beauty and necessity of every single member and constantly remind them how important they are to Stray Kids. There is likely no greater feeling for them than knowing that they have you by their side if they donâ€™t have anything else. The most important takeaway is the time they spend with you and the way you make them feel, and these are both filled with warm memories they can take with them for the rest of their lives. Youâ€™ve already spent some of the happiest and life-changing moments of your life with them, and there is still more to come. The members of Stray Kids, also your brothers and your family, couldnâ€™t have somebody who loves them any more than you do to look after them. You are always so considerate of them and their feelings and respond to them however they need. They are the best versions of themselves because of you and because you love them just the way they are. Now, they can go on to do whatever they aspire to because youâ€™ve encouraged them with that confidence. I want to personally thank your parents and family for raising you and helping you become the person you are today. I know they mean a lot to you, and that you couldnâ€™t be here doing what you are without their love and support. Because of them, you can use your platform to share with the world the same love that they have provided you with your whole life. I hope you never forget that they are always going to be the most proud of you no matter what you do. They love you most in this world and they do so in a way that nobody else understands. Stay love them as you do and we keep them in our hearts as we continue our time with you. We are so grateful to them for bringing you into the world, and for changing the world the same way that you do. Hyunjin, you touch each individual heart of every Stay, and this is easily one of the most charming parts about you. It is in your nature to make each and every Stay feel special, even if you donâ€™t know us personally. You welcome Stay from all around the world with open arms, and I felt as if I was a part of the family my whole life. You are so dedicated to your Stay and this is very apparent in everything that you do, whether it be performing or communicating with us directly. You have so much compassion for Stay and I feel like we are existing in our own separate world with you. Although we all live in different areas across the world, you take us to a place where we can all be one big family together, and it is one of the greatest feelings in the world. What you give to us is irreplaceable, and there could never be another person who helps us see the worth in ourselves the way you do. You also help us love one another. You influence others to treat others with kindness and Iâ€™ve met some of the most heartwarming Stay. I know that you help this family become closer every single day, and you remind us that if we have nothing else, we have each other. You invite us into your heart, the same way that you do your members, and you see qualities in us that we donâ€™t even see ourselves. I know for a fact that there are Stay who only believe in themselves because of you. You also share so much of yourself with us, and this is perhaps one of the biggest ways you can show somebody that you trust. As time goes on, I notice you revealing more of yourself through your music and just through direct conversation with your Stay. You have gotten so personal with us and this lets us know just how much you actually believe in us and trust us to keep these parts of you within our hearts. There is no greater honor than to have you place this vulnerable side of you in our hands, and we want to do the same for you. I know that it is not always easy to do this, so I hope you know that we could never mislead you or betray your trust if we wanted to. You are one of the most generous people we know, and we could not be here giving love to others and to you without the love that you gave us first. I know that youâ€™ve been through a lot, both personally, and professionally, and that your time as an idol has not always been easy or enjoyable. You have been active for several years now, but during your training period alone, youâ€™ve been met with demanding expectations, which many people cannot even say theyâ€™ve undergone. Just as your family is, Stay could not be more proud of you from overcoming your hardships and making it out on the brighter side. Each time you are met with a grueling time or task, thought it make time, you eventually endure through it until the end, and become more experienced. As Stay, I can say we learn so much from how you choose to release stress or convey how youâ€™re feeling through the mediums that provide you comfort.  We are beyond proud of you and continue to learn from you each day. I hope that this birthday makes all of your dreams come true, and you can take the time to truly celebrate who you are as a person. I know it might be difficult to focus on yourself, and if you find this to be the case, I hope you leave it to those who surround you and your admiring fans from all across the world to help you realize how revolutionary of a person you are. You are truly a gifted musician, and a courteous and selfless individual. You deserve this day, and every day that follows, to feel as appreciated as you truly are. I hope that every second is filled with memories that are unforgettable, and that this will be one of the greatest days that youâ€™ve had! Please have fun and celebrate in whatever way you choose, because your Stay will be cheering with you!  Thank you for sacrificing your time, efforts, pain, doubt, fear, tears, emotions, and physical boundaries just to bring us any content at all. For every effort that you put in that you might think is small, a Stayâ€™s mood or day is completely changed for the better. You are blessing to this world and continue to change it every day with how you choose to heal it and the people living in it. I hope you donâ€™t overwork yourself because you are perfect just the way you present yourself to us. We will support you and be there for you for the rest of our lives! I pray that you and your loved ones stay safe, and find happiness and worth in the future. Happy birthday Hyunjin, and we adore you so much!

author: @lovestxy
text:
My dearest Hyunjin,

Firstly let me start by expressing my heartfelt gratitude for all the joy and inspiration you have brought into my life As a loving fan you have meant more me than words can ever truly to convey

Your talent and dedication keeps amazing me Every stage performance every new release, and every effort you put into your craft has never failed to leave me in awe your hard work and perseverance have been a source of motivation for me to pursue my own dreams reminding me that with passion and determination anything is possible

But it is not just your music that has impacted me profoundly Your genuine kindness and humility shine through even amidst the unfathomable fame and success you have achieved Your willingness to use your platform to spread positivity and meaningful messages to your fans has touched my heart deeply
In my darkest moments your music has been a ray of light lifting my spirits and reminding me that I am not alone. Your lyrics have resonated with my own experiences giving me solace and a sense of belonging Your passion has become an escape for me a place where I can forget my worries and immerse myself in the magic you create.

I just wanted to take this moment to express my deepest appreciation for all that you have done for me and your countless fans around the world. Your genuine talent, hard work, kindness, and the impact you have made within the Kpop industry and beyond are truly remarkable. I am forever grateful to be able to witness your journey and be a part of your fandom.

Thank you, from the bottom of my heart, for being an inspiration and bringing so much happiness into my life. Please remember that, no matter what challenges you may face, your fans will always be here to support you
I love you â™¡

author: @Exolexterie
text:
At first I loved skz because they're so funny and talented. But this certain individual (Hyunjin) is something else. He personally inspires me to continue my passion in art and become an artist, and I also truly appreciate his outputs as an artist. I don't know him personally coz I'm only a fan but based on my intuition, I know he's full of love and vision. I am so lucky to exist the same timeline as him, seriously. I hope Hyunjin is having a happy personal life. You are born to create, Hyunjin. If someday he's going to put out his art gallery, I hope I am already rich that time! to travel! I would religiously take a whole day studying his brush strokes and color palette. He's not an 'ancestral' famous artist like Da Vinci but he's the only one Hwang Hyunjin in this world. I just appreciate him so much :-))) I was earlier listening to 2010's music and I felt like this song describe my feeling of longing earlier. Longing for the times that was innocent and simple. I loved being younger and pure. It's hard now because I feel like I already know much of this world. Fears, sadness is much harder and deeper than I was young. I hope Hyunjin continues to create as I will also continue to create my own artworks. He's a type of person I will talk about to other people when I grow older and older. I am really looking forward for his career to continue to bloom, same as to the other members of skz as they shine through their uniqueness and hardworksğŸ’Œ

author: @yj894
text:
â€œLet's JYPE hear us out and support Hyunjin.  If anyone who reads this and agrees, please cut and paste in your commentâ€

I am not a Stay, I am just an adult woman living in overseas, who happened to run into a Hyunjinâ€™s video clip on Youtube, gradually got to know him due to its algorithm and became interested in him. I'm worried, first of all, about Hyunjin how the recent situation will once again impact him mentally and emotionally.  So I'm posting here in hope that someone from JYPE can see this. 
I think the reason Hyunjinâ€™s past matter keeps rising to the surface is because JPYEâ€™s elementary response/problem solving was poor in the beginning. When I first look at the details of Hyunjin's bullying incident, I think it was not a school violence, but a â€œsituationâ€ that could easily happen between children in puberty. However, JPY saw business potential in Hyunjin, so they didnâ€™t kick him out, but instead, had Hyunjin write a personal but public apology which made it look as if Hyunjin truly committed and admitted the school violence.  This was all because JPYE was so conscious about their company image but not because they care about their artists like they claim, wasnâ€™t it?  
If you had decided to accept him in, JYPE should have fought the issue, made the public aware it wasnâ€™t a case of school violence/bullying.  As a result of your poor approach to the matter, those who are careless about Hyunjin would sabotage him in worst possible way and in every opportunity they have.  To me, Hyunjin is more a victim here than anyone else.  He is only a young talented person who loves to sing and dance and who is an inspiration to many people and kids in this world.  Please, clean up the issue thoroughly this time so that there are no more accusations against Hyunjin for the same incident in the future. Hyunjin is a person before he is a K-pop idol.

text: I've been listening to this song on repeat for twenty-four hours now and I can't get enough.... A charming, stunning voice, a sad whistle, a crying guitar, a drawing that exposes the soul... I want to hug you and save you from loneliness, Hyunjin... Every time I think that I love him so much that I won't be able to love him anymore, but with each new song, new painting, new dance, new photo, I immerse myself in these feelings deeper and stronger.... I will never get out of this web of feelings, because I got into this web voluntarily...  Hyunjin never ceases to amaze, delight and exult! May everything be fine with you, our talented, vulnerable, sensitive, beautiful in body and soul, little prince!  Hyunjin is the prince not only of Versace, but of the entire universe!

author: @lorenacarfaro
text:
Hyunjin, you might never read this, but I need you to know how it is for us.

We, true STAY. 
We, people from all around the world who feel grateful for meeting you guys.
We, who laugh when you laugh, and cry when you cry. 
We, who know stray kids has 8 members, love the 8 members and know it's 8 or nothing.
We, who love each one of your songs, but also the amount of love and care for each other. 
We, who don't imagine our lives without you guys. 
We, who promised forever. 
Who promised we'll STAY. 

For us, Stray Kids is our joy, our inspiration.
You are our friends, our family, the brothers we never had. 
Our love is real. And so is our loyalty. 

True STAY love Stray Kids. They protect them. They take care of them. 

True STAY don't go hating on the members (from SKZ or any other group).

True STAY don't force you to do things you don't feel confortable, don't demand information you choose to keep private and NEVER hurt you. 

True STAY might identify more with one or another, but always love the 8. 
We know it couldn't be different. 
You guys were meant to be.

True STAY are supportive and caring.

Because we understood the message. SKZ's message. 
We are authentic, caring, funny and unique.  

So, basically what I am saying is: 
RELY ON US. LET US BE YOUR SHIELD. WE WILL ALWAYS LOVE AND PROTECT YOU. 

Even if you ever make a mistake, we'll protect you. Not because you're perfect and we're blind, but because you're human and we love you. 

I know there is a lot of darkness out there, and sometimes being a huge success come with this unfair price of free hate. But let me remind you, it is worth it. 

What we are building here, it's worth it. 

We're making history. 
We're making art. 
We're shaking the world. 

So let's continue, together. 

When you're stray, we will STAY. FOREVER.

I know you're going through a lot right now and you'll probably never read this but I hope you know how truly loved you are.

 We are blessed to have you in our lives Hyunjin and Stray Kids...well, they would never be the same without you because you're a family. Scratch that, WE are a family and I promise that we've got your back.  The people sending those trucks and making hurtful comments aren't STAY because true STAY love you and know that you're a wonderful person.  

We adore you simply for being you. For being talented, kind, beautiful and creative. For being thoughtful, considerate, funny and caring. For being strong, resilient and hard working.  For making us smile every damn day. For laughing so hard we laugh too. For cheering us on when we're trying hard and offering comfort when we're struggling. 

STAY would give anything to comfort you now. To give you a hug and tell you that we're incredibly proud of you.  But all we can do is type messages of support and pray that it's enough - A

text: Hyunjin once again proving the fact that he has such an angelic voice. This song and the instrumentals, it gives me the feeling of losing something, yet longing to live in that moment forever. Like you were forced to part with something you love dearly, yet still being tethered to it by unsaid things. Hyunjin, you have got to be one of the most talented people out there. Your voice? 1000/10 (especially your laugh). Your art? always beautiful and creative. Your dancing? Man, you make me want to learn dance, just so I can understand the passion you have for it, cause it's like you control the music and you move so fluidly yet strong. So, yes. You are one of the most talented people out there and I still have not listed everything.

author: @WHAlice
text: Hyunjin, thank you for this song! Your songs, however, like all your works, are full of feelings and emotions, and it always finds such a response in me! This is probably the real art, when you don't just watch or listen, but feel and live every moment. When every part of your soul is sad, filled with delight or experiencing any other emotions. Thank you for giving us this opportunity, the opportunity to really feel. And you know, your voice is so good in this song! He conveys all the emotions, all the depth so well. You are a real treasure for art, you create not in order to make, but in order to live. And it makes me stay with you forever, because it's so rare in this world and so inspiring. Thank you for staying with us, and we will stay with you, our bright star!

author: @BloomzMember
text:
Oh my! ğŸ‘ğŸ‘ğŸ‘ Wonderful job to all that made this happen.
Hyunjin's voice ... soft, telling the story, then speaking slightly faster, explaining, almost a pleading. Then just... stopped.
The music! Also starting so softly, building simply, in volume and intensity, then the guitars - to me, the music itself represented how longing and love starts. And changes or ends.  There was a rawness, an edge brought by the mix of orchestra AND guitar that cleanly and clearly supported the message of the song.
Maybe it's because I'm older and have lived awhile, loved and lost.  Maybe it's because I'm on the way to the movies, by myself. 
...  I felt this song at my core! ...
Thank you Hyunjin and friends. I had a good cry and was incredibly grateful that someone else could relate to that feeling and express it so much better than I ever could.

author: @v__iiiaa
text:
I absolutely love the emotions Hyunjin has conveyed through this song. It's so raw, and like he is becoming more and more vulnerable as the song goes on. 
My interpretation is that it is about a relationship that is starting to fall out, the other may be distancing or has left, and the song represents the one that still wants to love the other, holding onto the memories they have made for one another. 
Whatever happens to a relationship, we still want to hold at least one thing, no matter what. That way we still have an indirect connection to something that once meant the world to us.

text:
I feel like i'm floating. I guess this was the kind of feeling i used to have when i was in love.
The more i listen, the more i fall, the more i understand, the more i realize that I'll always love this whole human being that Hyunjin is. 
How I cannot cheer or be proud of someone growing this much? Like how?
Im at the office working rn, crying and hoping that one day i can reach the top to see my goals accomplished, just like you writing lyrics, composing and now making the arrangements too. 
I love you so much that sometimes my heart doesn't understand that even if I go full-race while writing something, you may not even see it. 
Unilateral or fictional, it's a fact that i love you and i'm proud of everything you do, and it always be that way.
Thank you for being you, thru your lyrics, thru your feelings. ğŸ¤

author: @katyam601
text:
Hyunjin hi, I hope you'll see this.
The song "long for you" is very beautiful and touching. Hyunjin, you're on top as always. Such songs really suit you, you sing them so that tears come to your eyes. Lately, you've been accused of something you didn't do, and I'm very sorry for you. Those who spread this information are just jealous of you, don't pay attention to them. Your dancing, your charisma, your voice, your beauty, your sweet angelic smile, your laughter, your eyes - all these are your unique features that cannot be described in words. I just want to look at you and admire you. The "real, loyal" Stay love you, we will never let you (and other members) be offended. 
I've only been in the fandom for a few months, and now in this short period of time, I can say with certainty: You are everything to me!
You make me smile, in difficult moments, you support, you motivate. It has been very difficult for me lately (morally), but thanks to you, I managed to overcome this period, I looked at the world with different eyes, and I am very grateful to you for that. You just can't imagine how many people have become happy thanks to you. And we are very grateful to you for this, do not stop making us happy. If you are always supported, we will not go anywhere.
YOU MAKE STAY STAY.â¤

text: Even though you're a rapper, you can hit high notes. You are not human, hyunjin, you are an angel. You are perfect with your angelic voice, your eyes, your hair, your lips, your nose, your painting skills, your dance skills and everything else. That's why I call you angel. I mean this sincerely, even though you won't even notice my existence. Never give up, no matter what they say, stay strong and never forget STAY will always be with you. We will be with you whether you want it or not, we will not leave you. I think about you every year, every month, every week, every day, every hour, every minute, every second, every split second. I wonder what Hyunjin is doing right now? Is he okay? We truly love you, we value you, we are committed to you.I have posters in my room, I look at them every day and think if I will see them one day. You are a dream, hyunjin, I don't think I will ever see you, but I still don't give up on my dream, I live in Turkey, even if you won't read this, even if you can't come, I wanted you to know this. I love you with all my heart . Please don't leave us, just like we won't leave you. Please . I will forever protect you as much as I can, I will defend you no matter what.  I am writing this from the translation, sorry if there is any mistake . You told us "stray kids all around the world" in District 9, so please do as you say. We will never leave you, stay will never leave you.

text:
long for you by hyunjin

the sadness in your eyes
your voice so dry
when was the last time
we walked side by side

in the faded photo
I come across a smile
spread across youthful face
overlapped with the seaons

the night's so cold that it's almost unreal
I wake up in another silence
and I close my eyes

the white flower we planted together has bloomed
I do not dare pick it
now it withers away

so I long for you
and I long for you
and I'll long for you

so I can keep loving you so I could be loving you
and more
